  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/4fdc90da6c9522db86c6576654c4674f.webp?t=1773805100\" width=616 height=38 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/3f013226c6041350a11c75d99879970a.poster.avif?t=1773805100\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/3f013226c6041350a11c75d99879970a.webm?t=1773805100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/4fdc90da6c9522db86c6576654c4674f.webp?t=1773805100\" width=616 height=38 /></span><br><strong>GOT HIGH</strong> - Take on the crowd in thrilling brawl, race through labyrinthine traps in races, and battle it out in the arena in thrilling shooter action.<br>Three unique mini-games in one world full of action and challenges. Are you ready for this multi-level challenge?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/62e6a5d0d08a473f66eaacd1231da59f.poster.avif?t=1773805100\" width=720 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/62e6a5d0d08a473f66eaacd1231da59f.webm?t=1773805100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/62e6a5d0d08a473f66eaacd1231da59f.mp4?t=1773805100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/7e12326ee5d818756b1fc9554e0d6605.webp?t=1773805100\" width=616 height=38 /></span><br><br>Welcome to the world of adrenaline and speed! Get ready for an incredible combination of racing, fighting and shooting in our exciting game.<br>Feel the rhythm of battle on the road, where every turn can become a test, and every shot determines victory. Drive fast cars, fight opponents using the entire arsenal of weapons and a strategic approach.<br><br>The game offers a unique combination of dynamic racing tracks, exciting combat and unexpected turns of events.<br>Go through an adrenaline-pumping experience and show your skills in a unique survival race.<br><br>Immerse yourself in a world of speed, combat and endless possibilities. Welcome to an amazing journey where every second counts and victory depends on you.<br><br>Are you ready for this challenge? Ride through danger<br>fight for victory and become a legend in the world of racing and battle!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/4fdc90da6c9522db86c6576654c4674f.webp?t=1773805100\" width=616 height=38 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/a55ca2ddaf39efe93ffe93da67ce19f3.poster.avif?t=1773805100\" width=720 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/a55ca2ddaf39efe93ffe93da67ce19f3.webm?t=1773805100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/a55ca2ddaf39efe93ffe93da67ce19f3.mp4?t=1773805100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/4fdc90da6c9522db86c6576654c4674f.webp?t=1773805100\" width=616 height=38 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Variety of mini-games: Three unique game modes in one - fights with the crowd,<br>races with labyrinths-<br>traps and an arena for shooters.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dynamic Environments: Each mini-game takes place in dynamically changing environments,<br>offering a variety of challenges and unexpected situations.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gradual increase in difficulty: As you master each mini-game,<br>face increasing levels of complexity and challenges,<br>providing gradually increasing interest and motivation.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique Gameplay Styles: Each mini-game offers a unique play style,<br> suitable for different player preferences - from action and speed to tactics and strategy.<br>Attention! The game features boxing, shooting at people, and the ability to knock down a person on the track. <br>For some countries the game may be 18+.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/cf98a2d58546917e49aa26377e1eba12.poster.avif?t=1773805100\" width=720 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/cf98a2d58546917e49aa26377e1eba12.webm?t=1773805100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/cf98a2d58546917e49aa26377e1eba12.mp4?t=1773805100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642720/extras/4fdc90da6c9522db86c6576654c4674f.webp?t=1773805100\" width=616 height=38 /></span>",
